skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: camping fun
des: Camping Fun provides random fun ideas to remind everyone about the simple joys of nature and camping such as fishing, hiking, and building a camp fire. It also can provide a few safety reminders such as not to eat wild berries, and to stay away from snakes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
